        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/b/ecccb3/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2020-08-11T00:17:18.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>There is a decent about written on the history of winemaking and grape-growing in the Napa Valley, both before prohibition and during the boom in the late 60s / early 70s.  Is there anything worth reading on the history of Sonoma? Doesn\u2019t have to be a book: a history of a vineyard would also be interesting.  I love reading about sites that still have old-vine material on them today, or have been continuously farmed, but there just isn\u2019t much that I\u2019ve seen about Sonoma.</p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 10,
